1242001,"uid":244315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"切腹呀Sellmax"},{"pid":"cfb8de03c176ebdd27bb3a0860798ceaeaae8666","tid":1242001,"uid":71428,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"搞清楚我地既訴求唔係要佢道歉"},{"pid":"831a62a1876c63006560d219b4e964ffefd2c4f8","tid":1242001,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:20:19.000Z","msg":"！！緊急狀態！！請 大 家 停 止 打 飛 機！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1241948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1241948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請集中討論621<br />\nThank you"},{"pid":"bac16207e5d2e5ff31bdec866248d99142598732","tid":1242001,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cfb8de03c176ebdd27bb3a0860798ceaeaae8666","tid":1242001,"uid":71428,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"搞清楚我地既訴求唔係要佢道歉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:20:42.000Z","msg":"我講緊我地道歉 攻道德高地拎光環<br />\n唔係要林鄭道歉"},{"pid":"599f3ee6c5be2b07cb86c4f2460370776a9b27fe","tid":1242001,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於 追究黑警濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n先講建議：<br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a48f0af36295fb403af1cb6405c000719e86df","tid":1242001,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"大家可以同時做好多事<br />\n唔好拘泥於一種方法<br />\n我對大家要做既事係好開放的<br />\n只要符合抗爭原則"},{"pid":"5d9486e881eaa68cfbeb143d8799fe93abf2d6ae","tid":1242001,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b382ad0656844f439607edb13d4ca49e97f903ff","tid":1242001,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"有兩點可以考慮<br />\n1. 鞠躬<br />\n2. 幫趁受影響的商戶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"呢個 post 係回應緊 出面篇道歉文個 post"},{"pid":"d6ad092046ac157b9a81fd8639cd3d8956136270","tid":1242001,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d9486e881eaa68cfbeb143d8799fe93abf2d6ae","tid":1242001,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b382ad0656844f439607edb13d4ca49e97f903ff","tid":1242001,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"有兩點可以考慮<br />\n1. 鞠躬<br />\n2. 幫趁受影響的商戶"},"citedBy":1,"repl